33
00:02:18,805 --> 00:02:20,182
Ik herinner me dat.


34
00:02:21,725 --> 00:02:23,185
Ze stonden...


35
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,481
daar.


36
00:02:32,736 --> 00:02:34,821
